    <p>√© retornado <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">encontrado!</code>. Nessa situa√ß√£o, o operador <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">in</code> itera por todos os elementos de <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">s</code>, mesmo sem termos explicitamente estabelecido um la√ßo usando <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">while</code> ou <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">for</code>. Se a string <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">c</code> fizer parte de <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">s</code>, a condi√ß√£o <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">c in s</code> resultar√° em <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">True</code>.</p>
